# MagSpoof WebSerial module

- Serial writes go through `SerialClient.sendCommand()` only from user actions.
- Port track parsing from Vue (`trackParser.js`) — do not mix with LilyGO or Marauder parsers.
- MagSpoof has no platform upload or `device_source`.
- Document protocol changes in `docs/magspoof_v5_logic.md`.
- After edits: `dart format .`, `dart analyze`, `flutter test`.
